metadata.name: Metaseer's Prophecy, Genesis Edition #1
metadata.description:
###The Metaseer's Prophecy is a collaborative Metaverse story created by **T9Let and LeDrop WithCheese**. 
 The Metaseer's Prophecy is a story about a Metaseer who envisions LeDrop WithCheese arriving at the planet Gama with an abundance of magical cheese that not only feeds, but inspires a new community, creates happy palettes and opportunity for constituents. 
 This is the genesis edition storybook by T9Let and LeDrop WithCheese and will be the first in the series. 
 The Metaseer's Prophecy is one of the very first fully interactive, 3-D digital NFT storybooks published by **Metaverse Publishing.** 
 www.metaversepublishing.io
